steps.name: Given The user is successfully logged in the yieldWerx web application
When Click on "SWM" in the left menu bar
When Click "Automate SWM Policies" and new window will open
When Click on "Automate SWM Policy" and Create Automate SWM Policy window will open
When Select Source Facility as "WEB SMALL DATASET", Source Work Center as "WAFER SORT"
When Select the Source Device as "4670" and the Source Test Program as "PREBAKE_A_4670"
When Select the Target Facility as "WEB SMALL DATASET", Target Work Center as "WAFER SORT"
When Select the Target Device as "4670" and the Target Test Program as "POSTBAKE_A_4670"
When Select policy from Policies as "4670 Test Program" section and click on "Save" button
When SWM Policy has been created and displayed in "Automate SWM Policies" window
